    <p class="sm:ml-4 sm:mt-4 text-red-500 text-sm mb-8 sm:text-lg">For my introduction to JavaScript, I designed 'Duck Trump'â€”a game where the goal is to keep Trump thinking about rubber ducks instead of building walls.</p>
