 <section class="col-span-3 sm:w-[545px]">
    <h3 class="mt-4 sm:ml-4 sm:mt-12 text-red-500 text-3xl sm:text-3xl">03 Karrusel Festival</h3>
    <p class="sm:ml-4 sm:mt-4 text-red-500 text-sm mb-8 sm:text-lg">Karrusel Festival faces strong competition in the Danish festival scene. To stand out, it needed a clear design system, an intuitive artist overview, an accessible map, and a seamless ticket-buying experience.  </p>
